{"tid":1474690,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"當大家仲向到嘈緊逃犯條例時，林鄭已經修改緊中文科課程","createTime":"2019-08-15T09:17:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T03:51:25.000Z","uid":9160,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a336c561f646605884e23458c760f9db29a6ad6a","tid":1474690,"uid":9160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:17:14.000Z","msg":"當大家仲向到嘈緊逃犯條例時，林鄭已經修改緊中文科課程，唔洗聽同講廣東話了。<br />\n<br />\n16/9諮詢期就過啦，之後拿拿聲上立法會一讀二讀三讀搞點。DQ埋d阻頭阻勢既議員。香港人你慢慢嘈逃犯條例啦，日日食催淚彈啦。<br />\n<br />\n#滅一個文化先滅佢既語言<br />\n咁既政府管理香港，如果無左示威者，後果會係點？<br />\n示威者既爆力係唔岩，但哩個政府真係無得救。<br />\n你可以唔支持黃絲，但有一日香港失去核心價值時，唔好問點解。"},{"pid":"f3dae4f58b97fcecad09cd638a5ff4a8debc0722","tid":1474690,"uid":9160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:17:48.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"647006cbd89de492bcf0636757c82f6623b1c499","tid":1474690,"uid":9160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:20:20.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"cf2dd0b8faaaa4335a5f2d419deb67bdcccc9ea0","tid":1474690,"uid":9160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T10:59:56.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"5c2bdad3aeef583a1af55d7e970fceb4d39de2ca","tid":1474690,"uid":150325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:17:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b6c2bdda8c5423db309cdd0e9171ef71fbfa882c","tid":1474690,"uid":296952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:18:25.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">NOW OR NEVER</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dYUik2W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdYUik2W.jpg&h=b7b2e1de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hrs0znW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHrs0znW.png&h=d1fc316e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xqMkznX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxqMkznX.jpg&h=c5dabcdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1hvEPWh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1hvEPWh.jpg&h=f7d69869&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hEYbF2X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhEYbF2X.jpg&h=f6523fdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9TAab9D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9TAab9D.jpg&h=59c68e7f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f982a10f3a7924303008539ec09882174e41468","tid":1474690,"uid":263496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:15:21.000Z","msg":"有template啦，各位可以參考下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n專責小組成員謹啟：<br />\n<br />\n本人為香港市民，有聞 貴組於六月二十八日文件中提出刪去文憑試聆聽及說話考卷，本人堅表強烈反對，原因如下：<br />\n<br />\n一、掌握母語不等於能以母語表達，說話要言之有物、出口成文，除了要豐富的詞彙，亦要有清晰的表達方式，說話卷的核心價值在於檢視學生在日常用語之外，能否有效建構論點展開討論，而廢除後則無地方訓練學生這頂基本能力。<br />\n<br />\n二、掌握母語不等於能理解別人話語內容，聆聽別人的說話可以訓練學生將對話精煉的能力，亦即是捕捉重點的能力，假如廢除，恐怕學生會失去一個練習的平台，無法與人有效溝通。<br />\n<br />\n三、以語言系公開試ielts雅思為例，考核學生英語水平以讀聽寫說四考卷，尤其是以說話難度最高，一向是該考試衡量英語高水平者的好標準，如今 貴組研廢除聆、說二卷，猶如自斷一臂。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n綜合以上及眾多學者之言，冀 貴組於此項教育改革方向予於重新考慮。<br />\n<br />\n祝<br />\n教安<br />\n<br />\n一名香港市民上"},{"pid":"ce6ebaa9989ae963e333ac1cb26c859e580a2a88","tid":1474690,"uid":259786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:41:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a2ca8ac98cbbce398ef44d0904d2d48d542eee4","tid":1474690,"uid":181035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:59:48.000Z","msg":"推啊屌 點解冇人㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d2cc2e385c6a1203b44d913943f1066f3563457","tid":1474690,"uid":283494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T03:10:06.000Z","msg":"好大鑊, 大陸人更容易搶我地下一代d 人既飯碗,要比藍絲知道政府圖謀"},{"pid":"69e0dda54456dffa5e52a60fd3d6d8ef0510c8a1","tid":1474690,"uid":283494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T03:51:25.000Z","msg":"堆"}]}